item.title: Run Lab
item.description: Run Lab is a laboratory of running that offers live, interactive group workouts guaranteed to keep you fit. They help you stay accountable to running marathons, offering feedback from your coach and workouts available to you from anywhere in the world! I worked closely with the RunLab team, creating brand and communication strategy, a winning customer acquisition strategy for their business!
